ations SCE, outside, left side of front entrance from Halsted Street side (has a built in bicycle pump)  SCE, outside, left side of front entrance from campus side  Services Provided Portable Air Pump Bike Repair Tool Kit Rags/Towels available for clean-up  Note: In order to rent the bike tool kit or portable air pump, student or staff must leave icard or DL/State ID with the Building Manager.       SCW, Student Center West   Service Location 828 S. Wolcott Avenue, 312-413-5200 1st floor Building Manager’s service window  Services Provided Portable Air Pump Bike Repair Tool Kit  Note: In order to rent the bike tool kit or portable air pump, student or staff must leave icard or DL/State ID with the Building Manager.       SRF, Student Recreation Facility   Service Location 737 S. Halsted Street, 312-413-5150 1st floor equipment desk, (must swipe icard to gain entrance to building for fee paying members and current students)  Services Provided Bike Repair Tool Kit  Note: SRF only accepts icard or Visitor icard to rent the repair kit.          Services    Back to main content           Lockers    Bicycle Repair                  UIC Logo        Student Centers         Quick Links    Staff Directory    Student Employment    Feedback      Resources    Lockers Info and Policy    Bicycle Repair    Donation Bins      Tools    Building Directory    BM Reports    Operations Reports        BUTTON    Policies    Sustainability    Hours & Locations         Contact   scenters@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cooki